        {
            "author_association": "MEMBER",
            "body": "> I think we should do [#32287 (comment)](https://github.com/neovim/neovim/issues/32287#issuecomment-2835155023) instead of adding a new field as that will solve more use cases.\r\n\r\nWhat about both? This change looks pretty low-touch, and allows parts of the config to remain static, instead of fully dynamic?",
